  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baa\u0baf \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc7 \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "All problems can be solved only if President Gotabaya steps down - Rajitha",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "We will be involved in the struggle against the government from July 9. Only if President Gotabaya Rajapaksa resigns, all problems can be solved.",
        "The President is not clear about the people's problem and insistence. The health infrastructure of the country is completely affected.",
        "Former Health Minister Rajitha Senaratne told the House that there is no medicine in the government hospitals, and if you go to a private hospital, you will feel bad about the medical fees.",
        "He mentioned the above in a comment following the adjournment debate when Parliament met on Wednesday 6th under the chairmanship of the Speaker.",
        "Due to the mismanagement of the Podujana Peramuna-led government, including the President, the fuel supply infrastructure has been completely affected and basic sectors including education, health and transport have been affected.",
        "As the middle class has lost its industry due to the fuel crisis, the unemployment rate may increase in the future.",
        "The government has no short and long term plan for the basic problems that have their origin in the social structure.",
        "The Minister of Power mentions in the House that the fuel tanker will arrive but the fuel tanker does not arrive, the queue for fuel is long and the number of deaths is increasing.",
        "The Minister of Commerce mentioned in the meeting that there will be no shortage of essential items and the necessary food items are in stock.",
        "But there is a shortage of products in the market and shops. It is seen that we will have to face food shortage in the future.",
        "According to UNICEF, Sri Lanka's health sector, which was seen at its best, is going under threat.",
        "According to the evaluation of the Unisen company regarding the current situation of the country, 22 percent of the total population has skipped getting food and 86 percent have skipped the time of eating.",
        "58 percent of the total population should be given relief on humanitarian basis, and 17 percent are under observation and will face a massive crisis if these problems are not resolved.",
        "By 2022, 17 lakh children are undernourished following a 50 percent decline in agricultural productivity.",
        "Private hospitals are functioning without any supervision. 112 lakhs have been charged for brain surgery in private hospitals.",
        "There is a shortage of medicines in government hospitals, if you go to a private hospital, you will see the fee and the mood will be affected.",
        "The President does not know that the country is facing serious crises. The President has no concern about the suffering of the people.",
        "He is in hiding. He is irresponsible when the entire country, including religious leaders, insists that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa is unfit to hold office.",
        "Tens of thousands of people will gather in Colombo the day after tomorrow against the government. We will be united in the people's struggle."
      ],
